<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>A股每日预测报告 — $report_date</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
         background: #f5f5f5; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
  .container { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.3em; border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 6px;
       margin: 24px 0 12px; }
  h3 { font-size: 1.05em; margin: 16px 0 8px; color: #555; }
  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px;
          box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08); margin-bottom: 16px; }

  /* 今日一句话总结 */
  .today-summary {
    background: #fff7e6;
    border-left: 4px solid #fa8c16;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }
  .today-summary h2 { border-color: #fa8c16; color: #ad6800; margin: 0 0 10px 0; }
  .today-summary .summary-line { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 16px; }
  .today-summary .honesty { color: #d4380d; font-weight: bold; }

  /* 诚信声明 */
  .disclaimer {
    background: #fff3cd; border: 2px solid #e6a817;
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .disclaimer h2 { border-color: #e6a817; color: #856404; }
  .disclaimer ul { margin-left: 20px; color: #856404; }
  .disclaimer .metrics { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 8px; }
  .disclaimer .metric-val { font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: bold; color: #c0392b; }
  .disclaimer .metric-lbl { font-size: 0.8em; color: #666; }
  .disclaimer .metric-translation { font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f5800; margin-top: 2px; }

  /* 今日总览 4 格 */
  .summary-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px;
                  margin-bottom: 16px; }
  @media(max-width:640px){ .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
  .summary-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px;
                  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08); text-align: center; }
  .summary-card .big { font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; color: #2c7be5; }
  .summary-card .lbl { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-top: 4px; }
  .summary-card.ok .big { color: #27ae60; }
  .summary-card.warn .big { color: #e67e22; }
  .summary-card.err .big { color: #c0392b; }

  /* 信号分布彩色横条 */
  .signal-distribution { margin: 8px 0; }
  .signal-bar { display: block; padding: 6px 12px; margin: 4px 0;
                min-width: 80px; color: white; font-weight: bold;
                border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }
  .signal-bar.buy  { background: #52c41a; }
  .signal-bar.sell { background: #f5222d; }
  .signal-bar.hold { background: #bfbfbf; color: #333; }

  /* 信号表格 */
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; }
  th { background: #f0f4ff; padding: 7px 10px; text-align: left;
       border-bottom: 2px solid #c5d3e8; }
  td { padding: 6px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tr:hover td { background: #f9f9f9; }
  td small { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; margin-left: 4px; }
  .tag-buy  { display:inline-block; background:#d4edda; color:#155724;
              border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:.8em; }
  .tag-sell { display:inline-block; background:#f8d7da; color:#721c24;
              border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:.8em; }
  .tag-hold { display:inline-block; background:#e2e3e5; color:#383d41;
              border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:.8em; }
  .tag-tp   { display:inline-block; background:#d4edda; color:#155724;
              border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:.8em; }
  .tag-sl   { display:inline-block; background:#f8d7da; color:#721c24;
              border-radius:4px; padding:2px 8px; font-size:.8em; }

  /* ASCII 条图（备用） */
  .ascii-bar { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85em;
               background: #f8f9fa; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 6px;
               white-space: pre; overflow-x: auto; }

  /* 📖 大白话段 */
  .plain-language {
    background: #f6ffed;
    border-left: 3px solid #52c41a;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin: 16px 0 24px 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .plain-language .emoji { font-size: 18px; margin-right: 6px; }

  /* 状态标记 */
  .status-ok   { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
  .status-warn { color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold; }
  .status-err  { color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold; }

  /* 元数据 */
  .meta { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-top: 8px; }
  .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.75em; color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
  .section-label { font-size: 0.75em; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
                   color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 4px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <h1>📅 A股每日预测报告</h1>
  <p class="meta">预测日期：$report_date &nbsp;|&nbsp; 股票池：$universe_size 只 &nbsp;|&nbsp; 生成时间：$generated_at</p>

  <!-- ===== 今日一句话总结（最显眼位置，第一眼看到）===== -->
  <div class="today-summary">
    <h2>🎯 今日一句话总结</h2>
    <p class="summary-line">$summary_line_1</p>
    <p class="summary-line">$summary_line_2</p>
    <p class="summary-line honesty">$summary_line_3</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== 诚信声明（红线，永远不可省略）===== -->
  <div class="disclaimer">
    <h2>⚠️ 诚信声明 —— 请在查看预测前仔细阅读</h2>
    <div class="metrics">
      <div>
        <div class="metric-val">AUC = $direction_auc</div>
        <div class="metric-lbl">明日强势评分（随机猜 AUC=0.5）</div>
        <div class="metric-translation">$auc_translation</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric-val">R² = $return_r2</div>
        <div class="metric-lbl">收益率预测（猜均值 R²=0）</div>
        <div class="metric-translation">$r2_translation</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric-val">rank-IC ≈ $ranking_ic</div>
        <div class="metric-lbl">横截面排名（有效 IC &gt; 0.05）</div>
        <div class="metric-translation">$ic_translation</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric-val">macro-F1 = $signal_f1</div>
        <div class="metric-lbl">买卖信号（基线 F1≈0.33）</div>
        <div class="metric-translation">$f1_translation</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul style="margin-top:12px;">
      <li>以上模型验证集指标均接近随机基线，<strong>不具备 alpha</strong></li>
      <li>本报告所有信号<strong>不构成任何投资建议</strong>，仅供量化学习研究使用</li>
      <li>过去的回测表现不代表未来实盘收益</li>
      <li>A股 T+1 规则：今日买入明日才能卖出</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== §1 今日总览 ===== -->
  <h2>§1 今日总览</h2>
  <div class="summary-grid">
    <div class="summary-card $direction_status_cls">
      <div class="big">$direction_status_icon</div>
      <div class="lbl">① 明日强势评分</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card $return_status_cls">
      <div class="big">$return_status_icon</div>
      <div class="lbl">② 预期收益</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card $ranking_status_cls">
      <div class="big">$ranking_status_icon</div>
      <div class="lbl">③ 横截面排名</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-card $signal_status_cls">
      <div class="big">$signal_status_icon</div>
      <div class="lbl">④ 买卖信号</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <p>本次覆盖 <strong>$universe_size 只</strong>股票，使用 <strong>$model_version</strong> 模型。</p>
    <p class="meta">数据截至：$data_cutoff &nbsp;|&nbsp; 模型文件：$model_paths</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== §2 ① 明日强势评分 ===== -->
  <h2>§2 ① 明日强势评分（DirectionModel）</h2>
  $direction_section

  <!-- ===== §3 ② 预期收益 ===== -->
  <h2>§3 ② 预期收益率（ReturnRegressor）</h2>
  $return_section

  <!-- ===== §4 ③ 横截面排名 ===== -->
  <h2>§4 ③ 横截面排名 Top N（RankingModel）</h2>
  $ranking_section

  <!-- ===== §5 ④ 买卖信号 ===== -->
  <h2>§5 ④ 买卖点信号（TradeSignalModel）</h2>
  $signal_section

  <!-- ===== §6 历史准确率（P14 落盘后可用）===== -->
  <h2>§6 历史准确率</h2>
  <div class="card">
    $accuracy_section
  </div>

  <!-- ===== §7 运行元数据 ===== -->
  <h2>§7 运行元数据</h2>
  <div class="card">
    <table>
      <tr><td><strong>报告生成时间</strong></td><td>$generated_at</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>总耗时</strong></td><td>$total_seconds 秒</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>数据截至日</strong></td><td>$data_cutoff</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>股票池规模</strong></td><td>$universe_size 只</td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>模型文件路径</strong></td><td><code>$model_paths</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>预测 JSON 落盘</strong></td><td><code>$json_path</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><strong>运行错误</strong></td><td>$errors_summary</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    A股量化预测学习项目 · 仅供学习 · 不构成投资建议<br>
    generated by astock-quant Stage 4 P13
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
